alias Filter db

alias InputPressure r1
alias Filter1Damage r2
alias Filter2Damage r3
alias FiltersDamage r4

define IceCrusherHash 443849486

Start:
yield
s Filter Mode 1
ls Filter1Damage Filter 0 Quantity
ls Filter2Damage Filter 1 Quantity
add FiltersDamage Filter1Damage Filter2Damage
div FiltersDamage FiltersDamage 2
ble FiltersDamage 1 FiltersDamaged
l InputPressure Filter PressureInput
bgt InputPressure 45000 StopCrushers
ble InputPressure 40000 StartIceCrushers
j Start

FiltersDamaged:
s Filter On 0
sb IceCrusherHash On 0
j Start

StopCrushers:
sb IceCrusherHash On 0
j Start

StartIceCrushers:
sb IceCrusherHash On 1
j Start
